{"tid":1047331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利記頭痕 比利貼紅軍贏英超冠軍","createTime":"2019-03-05T01:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T09:14:02.000Z","uid":94771,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"80a6d23dc7fb08167365a106c6096a207e4f1192","tid":1047331,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hMNuyXU2CsRjFS3IEw8SQA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzUwO2g9MjMwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/Goal.com/6387822_hp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhMNuyXU2CsRjFS3IEw8SQA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzUwO2g9MjMwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2FGoal.com%2F6387822_hp.jpg&h=4d042883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n羅拔臣指壓力在曼城身上<br />\n<br />\n雖然紅軍剛失去榜首之位，以1分落後曼城，但比利仍對他們充滿信心，他周一在Twitter祝賀紅軍名將杜格利殊時說︰「祝紅軍英雄杜格利殊生日快樂，我由開始至今仍相信利物浦可贏得英超冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n對於得到比利的「祝賀」，利迷或許不是味兒，是關他素有「烏鴉口」之稱，經典事例便有他曾預言非洲球隊可在2000年贏得世盃冠軍，但相隔十多年後非洲球隊至今仍未曾打入4強，而在去年俄羅斯世盃更未有一隊可出線16強。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHappy birthday to Liverpool hero, Kenny Dalglish. I backed @LFC to win the Premier League from the start. I still think they will do it. // Feliz anivers&aacute;rio para o her&oacute;i do Liverpool, @kennethdalglish. Eu apoiei o @LFC no in&iacute;cio da Premier League e ainda acho que levar&atilde;o a ta&ccedil;a. <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/QemLKYzJo2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FQemLKYzJo2&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=c3964dbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/QemLKYzJo2</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Pel&eacute; (@Pele) March 4, 2019<br />\n其他例子尚有他在2002世盃曾預測巴西未能在分組賽出線，但最終巴西贏得冠軍；以及同屆賽事他估計中國可出線16強，但最終在分組3戰全敗未入一球。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak2sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=f4a8e30c\" data-auto-link targe